Scope
-----

The commercial licence from Softside Tech covers the
bilbycast-gateway-sdk source code only. Softside does not hold
copyright in third-party Rust crates this SDK depends on (tokio,
tokio-tungstenite, rustls, serde, etc.) and cannot relicense them.
Those crates are distributed under their own permissive licences
(MIT / Apache-2.0 / BSD-3-Clause / ISC — see Cargo.lock) and remain
available under those terms in both AGPL and commercial builds.
